      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIG BOY PANTS (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (22.41) at Warrnambool behind Paw Qwerty in a Mix 6/7. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. The form out of his last race has been franked. Leading chance again. PAW DANGER (7) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (22.63) last time in a Mix 6/7 at Warrnambool. Has never missed the frame here from three starts. Great chance to atone. PROCYON (2) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in three starts, including two wins. Placed last time (22.52) at Shepparton in a Mix 6/7, finishing second and beaten 1.3 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. ROTHWELL JACK (4) hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a Rank Limit - Restricted Win at this track over 400m.",
